summary: THE KICKSTAND ON THE MOTORCYCLE CAME DOWN WHILE DRIVING, WHICH CAUSED THE DRIVER TO LOSE CONTROL.  THE DRIVER IS CURRENTLY IN THE HOSPITAL.  THERE WAS A DEFECT IN THE KICKSTAND SPRING.  AMERICAN IRONWORKS TEJAS 2003.  THE DEALER AND MANUFACTURER WAS PREVIOUSLY AWARE OF DEFECT AND FAILED TO HAVE RECALL (AMERICAN IRONHORSE TEJAS 2003).     *CB
